823
00:47:49.069 --> 00:47:52.104
Suddenly, I'm very glad
I paid you to tag along.

824
00:47:52.106 --> 00:47:55.006
[Groaning]

825
00:47:55.008 --> 00:47:56.274
Mason!

826
00:47:56.276 --> 00:47:57.645
Unh!
Aah!

827
00:47:59.547 --> 00:48:01.179
Where is Venegas?

