846
00:49:25.600 --> 00:49:27.635
Jorge:
Colonel Koehorst.

847
00:49:34.642 --> 00:49:37.309
General Vásquez,

848
00:49:37.311 --> 00:49:39.211
my clients are very
disappointed that

849
00:49:39.213 --> 00:49:42.047
your uncle is still alive
and causing trouble.

850
00:49:42.049 --> 00:49:44.382
It would appear that
your men likewise

851
00:49:44.384 --> 00:49:46.218
